rows.name: Paragraph
rows.text:
My sisters the weavers of destiny, the Norns, spin the thread for every single person on earth. You and I, we spin the thread of your own story. Create your own roleplaying world with me. No matter if you just want the background story for your own character, if you came up with a fancy monster, if you forged a special item, or if you want to put a whole adventure on paper with me, all that is possible.

I'm still not quite as big a deal as my divine big sisters, but together with you I'll outgrow myself and outshine everything you've seen so far. How is that going to happen? Well, with me everything is easier. Go ahead and try it out!

rows.name: Note
rows.text:
Not satisfied with the planned features?

No problem, get in touch with us on Reddit! (u/sauriel_rpg)

rows.name: Heading
rows.text: Spin the thread of your story with me.

monster.name: Norn

specialTraits.name: Legendary Resistance (9/day)
specialTraits.description: If Norn fails a saving throw, she may choose to make it instead.

specialTraits.name: Spin thread
specialTraits.description: Norn has advantage on Charisma and Dexterity saving throws.

ability.name: Golden Scissors
ability.description:
All creatures of Nora's choice within 99m of Nora that are aware of her must make a Wisdom saving throw against DC 19 to avoid being frightened for 1 minute.

A creature can reroll the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself if successful. It suffers disadvantage on the saving throw if Norn is still in sight. If the saving throw succeeds or the effect ends, then the creature is immune to golden scissors for the next 24 hours.

ability.name: Ponder
ability.description: Norn can innately cast the Friendship spell, with no components required. The attribute for casting innate spells is Wisdom for her.

attack.name: Claws
attack.attack: +19 to hit, range 30 ft., one target

monster.legendaryDescription: Nora can perform 9 legendary actions and choose from the following options. She can only use one legendary action option at a time, and only at the end of another character's turn. Nora regains spent legendary actions at the beginning of her turn.

legendaryActions.name: Past
legendaryActions.description: Norn looks back to the days when it was difficult to create his character.

legendaryActions.name: Future
legendaryActions.description: Nora is looking forward to working with you on your project.
